Pepyatka password reset
------------------------

Thank you for using Pepyatka. We received a password reset request
for this email address (<%= user.email %>) on
https://try.pepyatka.com/. To reset your password, click the link below:

https://try.pepyatka.com/account/reset?token=<%= user.resetPasswordToken %>

If you did not request a password reset, then someone probably
mis-typed their email address. You can ignore this message, and we
apologize for the inconvenience.

If you have any problems resetting your password, you can get help
from us at mail@pepyatka.com.

